markdownRemark.html: To note 34: Angela Nuovo's 2003 work, Il commercio librario, has now been superseded by her fully revised, enlarged, and updated The Book Trade in the Italian Renaissance, Leiden, Brill, 2013.The discussion cited here appears in the English version of her book at pp. 101-105 and 332-335.
